Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
GENTYPE_OMNI = 1 GENTYPE_SPOT = 2 GENTYPE_AREA = 3 GENTYPE_INFINITE = 4 GENTYPE_IES = 5
LIGHTGROUP_GENERAL_LIGHT = 1 LIGHTGROUP_BUILTIN_OMNI = 2 LIGHTGROUP_BUILTIN_SPOT = 3 LIGHTGROUP_BUILTIN_VIS_AREA = 4 LIGHTGROUP_BUILTIN_NONVIS_AREA = 5
! TabIDs TABID_ROOT = -1 TABID_BASIC_PARAMS = 100 TABID_CUSTOM = 110 TABID_FLOORPLAN = 120 TABID_MODEL = 130 TABID_FPLAN_MODEL = 140 TABID_EFFECTS = 300 TABID_VIS_LIGHT = 310 TABID_NOISE = 320 TABID_CAUSTICS = 330 TABID_LENS_FLARE = 340 TABID_CLIPPING = 350 TABID_ILLUM_FX = 360 TABID_SURFACE_FX = 370 TABID_LISTPARAMS = 400
dim uiUsedPageIDs[][2] dim uiUsedPageNames[][2]
idxPage = 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Основные Параметры Света` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_Light_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_BASIC_PARAMS : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_ROOT
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Отображение в 3D и на Плане Этажа` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_FPLAN_MODEL : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_BASIC_PARAMS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Эффекты` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightEffects_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_EFFECTS : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_ROOT
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Шум` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightNoise_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_NOISE : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_EFFECTS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Каустики` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightCaustics_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_CAUSTICS : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_EFFECTS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Блики на Линзах` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightLensFlare_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_LENS_FLARE : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_EFFECTS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Спецэффекты, связанные с Освещением` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightIllumFx_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_ILLUM_FX : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_EFFECTS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Спецэффекты, связанные с Тенями и Покрытиями` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_LightSurfaceFx_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_SURFACE_FX : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_EFFECTS
idxPage = idxPage + 1
uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][1] = `Параметры Спецификаций` : uiUsedPageNames[idxPage][2] = "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)" uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][1] = TABID_LISTPARAMS : uiUsedPageIDs[idxPage][2] = TABID_ROOT
file_dependence "uiTab_Light_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightEffects_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightNoise_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightCaustics_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightLensFlare_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightIllumFx_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_LightSurfaceFx_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
dim pageValues[] for i = 1 to vardim1(uiUsedPageIDs) pageValues[i]= uiUsedPageIDs[i][1] next i
